Cute story, but it is so boring, this is why people say Vanilla sucks. As part of a bigger story, scenes like this would be fine, but as fap material ? Its fucking weak, there is many great "vanilla" hentai doujin out there, with both hot sex, art, sweet story, and a good ending. This however is not one of them, the story is the typical run of the mill vanilla fast food and the art  and scenario isn't "erotic" or "sexy" at all. The sex is not a focal point of the story, it is just a vehicle to further push along the plot and not vice versa, therein lies the problem.  

A good ero doujin puts a lot of emphasis on the actual sex and emotions of the participating parties, the story is just there to further enhance the sex scenes. This is how anything from "vanilla" to netorare can be a huge turn on for people depending on preference, regardless of the genre and tags. That is why some people say netorare is "better" than vanilla, because the story is typically more in service to the sex.
